subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Karrie Webb, the defending champion, and Lorie Kane each shot a three-under-par 69 to share the lead after two rounds of the Longs Drugs Challenge in Danville, Calif. Lorena Ochoa was a stroke back after shooting a 70. Webb and Kane had totals of six-under 138 at Blackhawk Country Club.
